# Independent Drive – Park Reservation Tool

All Rights Reserved © 2025 Independent Drive Team

---

## 🌍 Map Data Usage

This project uses disc golf course location data extracted from **OpenStreetMap (OSM)** via the **Overpass API**.

- © OpenStreetMap contributors  
- Data available under the **Open Database License (ODbL)**  
- API Used: [Overpass API](https://overpass-api.de/)

We gratefully acknowledge the work of the OpenStreetMap community in making this data publicly available.

---

## 💻 Frontend Notes

 portions of the frontend code (HTML, CSS, JavaScript) were generated or assisted by artificial intelligence (AI) tools to help accelerate development.

Other parts of the interface and layout were influenced by external educational tutorials (see References below).

All custom design, features, styling, and written content were created by the Independent Drive development team.

---

## 🧩 APIs, Tools & Libraries Used

- **Fuse.js** – Fuzzy search functionality  
  [https://fusejs.io](https://fusejs.io)

- **OpenWeatherMap API** – Real-time weather data for park locations  
  [https://openweathermap.org/api](https://openweathermap.org/api)

- **Google Fonts: Montserrat** –  
  Licensed under the Open Font License  
  [https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Montserrat](https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Montserrat)

- **Google Maps Embed**  
  Subject to [Google Maps Terms of Service](https://developers.google.com/maps/terms)

- **Icons from Google Material Icons** – Used under the [Apache 2.0 License](https://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0)

- **Voice Search Web Speech API** – Built-in browser feature for accessibility support

- **OpenAI ChatGPT API** – Used to power the Parky chatbot, an AI assistant for helping users with reservation questions  
  [https://platform.openai.com](https://platform.openai.com)


