---

## 🧠 Chatbot Integration

This project includes a custom-built AI chatbot widget called **Parky**.

- Built using the **OpenAI ChatGPT API**
- Dynamically loaded and embedded using HTML/CSS/JavaScript
- Responds to user input about park policies, reservation steps, and availability
- Designed to improve accessibility and support across all pages

Parky does **not** store or log any personal data. It's integrated only to assist visitors with common questions.

